%N A397717 Convolution of hyperfactorials and superfactorials.
%F A397717 a(n) = Sum_{k=0..n} A002109(k)*A000178(n-k).
%F A397717 a(n) ~ A * n^(n*(n+1)/2 + 1/12) / exp(n^2/4), where A is the Glaisher-Kinkelin constant A074962.
%t A397717 Table[Sum[BarnesG[k+2]*Hyperfactorial[n-k], {k, 0, n}], {n, 0, 12}]
